videos.description: With the clock winding down, Oregon's Will Richardson puts his defender in the blender with a spin move and draws the foul as he sinks the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Oregon's Richardson uses spin move to get and-1 finish) 2019/12/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon's Richardson uses spin move to get and-1 finish

videos.description: Payton Pritchard comes up with the steal and finds Anthony Mathis in transition to knock down a big 3-pointer, giving Oregon a 54-53 lead over Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mathis sinks clutch 3 for Oregon lead) 2019/12/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mathis sinks clutch 3 for Oregon lead

videos.description: Anthony Mathis tries to beat the buzzer with a last second 3-pointer, but he doesn't get it off in time, sending the game into overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mathis can't beat the last-second buzzer) 2019/12/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mathis can't beat the last-second buzzer
